WEBVTT

00:02:57.800 --> 00:03:00.080
Mike lost his job to a machine.

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:04.896
87 percent of lost manufacturing jobs

00:03:04.920 --> 00:03:07.736
have been eliminated
because we've made improvements

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:10.320
in our own productivity
through automation.

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:16.416
So that means that one out of 10
lost manufacturing jobs

00:03:16.440 --> 00:03:18.720
was due to offshoring.

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:22.096
Now, this is not just a US phenomenon.

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:23.336
No.

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:26.696
In fact, automation is spreading
to every production line

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:28.640
in every country around the world.

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:31.336
But look, I get it: